Package: com.mk.runningdotindicator
Name: RunningDotIndicator
Version: 1.3.6
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: Adds a customizable indicator dot beside app icons on the home screen to show which apps are currently running (process-based detection). Color, shape, size, position and opacity are all configurable.
Maintainer: 口非口
Author: 口非口
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
Homepage: https://codebuddy.cn
